From: Xi Wang <wangxi11@huawei.com>
Date: Mon, 13 Apr 2020 19:58:10 +0800
Subject: RDMA/hns: Support 0 hop addressing for SRQ buffer
Patch-mainline: v5.8-rc1
Git-commit: 6fd610c5733d0b2024393e82f145180324ef55a7
